Norwarden: Foes of the Free People
Foes of the Free Peoples found at Norwarden should be defeated in order protect those within the Wildwood.
Foes can be found at Norwarden in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Norwarden.
Foes of the Free Peoples have claimed the tower of Norwarden within the Wildwood. Defeating their numbers here will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
